113 commission.
114 (d) A member who has failed to attend three consecutive
115 properly noticed meetings may be removed at the request of the
116 commission."
117 Section 4. The Legislature concurs in the
118 recommendations of the Sunset Committee as provided in
119 Sections 1, 2, and 3.
120 Section 5. This act shall become effective immediately.
Page 5

